'''Bedoukian反应'''（Bedoukian reaction）

在[[对甲苯磺酸|对甲苯磺酸]]或[[乙酸钾|乙酸钾]]存在条件下，[[醛|醛]]或[[酮|酮]]与[[乙酸酐|乙酸酐]]共热得到[[烯醇|烯醇]][[乙酸|乙酸]][[酯|酯]]，它在[[四氯化碳|四氯化碳]]中[[溴化|溴化]]得到加成物，经[[醇解|醇解]]得到[[缩醛|缩醛]]，最后用酸水解缩醛，得到 α-溴代醛或酮。<ref>{{cite journal en|title=Synthesis of Bromoacetals|author=Paul Z. Bedoukian|journal=[[J._Am._Chem._Soc.|J. Am. Chem. Soc.]]|year=1944|volume=66|issue=4|pages=651–652|doi=10.1021/ja01232a501}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal en|title=A New Synthesis of α-Bromoaldehydes|author=Paul Z. Bedoukian|journal=[[J._Am._Chem._Soc.|J. Am. Chem. Soc.]]|year=1944|volume=66|issue=8|pages=1325–1327|doi=10.1021/ja01236a037}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal en|title=Preparation of α,β-Unsaturated Aldehyde Dimethyl Acetals and their Free Aldehydes
|author=Paul Z. Bedoukian|journal=[[J._Am._Chem._Soc.|J. Am. Chem. Soc.]]|year=1957|volume=79|issue=4|pages=889–892|doi=10.1021/ja01561a028}}</ref>

